## 13. Split into cases
### Example
```coq
Lemma example_cases :
  ‚àÄ x ‚àà ‚Ñù, ‚àÄ y ‚àà ‚Ñù,
    max(x, y) = x ‚à® max(x, y) = y.
Proof.
```

```coq
Take x ‚àà (‚Ñù).
Take y ‚àà (‚Ñù).
Either (x < y) or (x ‚â• y).
- Case (x < y).
  It suffices to show that (max(x, y) = y).
  We conclude that (max(x, y) = y).
- Case (x ‚â• y).
  It suffices to show that (max(x, y) = x).
  We conclude that (max(x, y) = x).
Qed.
```
